367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F074607_70a290bc567b6a800d924d301382d367.jpg&h=a5ec3e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪依張？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我一直唔撚明, 話班大陸人係高樓價原因.<br />\n點解唔拉返果班賣樓比大陸人既仆街公審.<br />\n<br />\n同埋 d 大陸人用咩身份移民, 加拿大係咪一到步就可以免費享用服務? 同埋有錢既加拿大本土人係咪唔可以或者要比錢先可以享用服務.<br />\n<br />\n最後加拿大點計稅?"},{"pid":"47fbff42270df8761728f6dd020a68fd58650707","tid":16534,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a46669cad30a0d76ebb0806e81af67bcff6c9f8","tid":16534,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:04:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc5405004921d285bcd76a1b53bcc3ecb329451a","tid":16534,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時到香港派單張？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港仲慘呀! 加國只係畀富蝗侵蝕, HK無論上中下各階層皆被吸血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f609c79acd8913bb64d06ee03ca11776d90cbbc3","tid":16534,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成班死蝗蟲影衰全華人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地係香港人<br />\n我地係廣東人<br />\n我地唔係華人</blockquote><br />\n雖然不想承認，但個情況就好似我地睇印度佬同巴基佬咁"},{"pid":"f1bc91481ce395c9787caa6baf6bd56f6d34656e","tid":16534,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"幾時排華"},{"pid":"87846c570984794d8d966682b932c33339f69411","tid":16534,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"劉先生欺善怕惡，呢種國家個政治斯文，咪敢上街出聲囉"},{"pid":"56315eddcb39c2482fe08b4321e826e6cc1f4d3f","tid":16534,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉先